Sunway Sitges International (2019), Round 6
Sicilian, Sozin, Benko variation (B57)

1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 d6 4. d4 cxd4 5. Nxd4 Nf6 6. Bc4 Qb6 7. Ndb5 a6 8. Be3 Qa5 9. Nd4 e6 10. O-O Be7 11. Bb3 Nxd4 12. Bxd4 O-O 13. Qd3 b5 14. a3 Bb7 15. f4 Rac8 16. Kh1 Qd8 17. Rae1 Re8 18. Re2 Bf8 19. Qh3 d5 20. e5 Ne4 21. f5 Nc5 22. f6 Nxb3 23. cxb3 a5 24. Re3 b4 25. fxg7 Bxg7 26. Rg3 Re7 27. Rf4 bxc3 28. Qh6 Qf8 29. Rh4 f5 30. Qxh7+ Kf7 31. Qg6+ Kg8 32. Rgh3

The 6th Sunway Sitges International is a 10-round Swiss open taking place from 13-22 December 2019 in the Hotel Sunway Playa Golf & Spa in Sitges, Spain.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.sunwaychessfestival.com
